sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Web/Mobile Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Payment as Payment Service

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/orders
    Gateway->>Auth: Validate JWT Token
    Auth-->>Gateway: Token Valid (User ID: 123)

    Gateway->>Order: Create Order Request

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Order,Inventory: Saga Pattern Initiation
        Order->>Inventory: Reserve Items
        alt Inventory Available
            Inventory-->>Order: Reservation Success
            Order->>Payment: Process Payment

            alt Payment Success
                Payment-->>Order: Payment Confirmed
                Order-->>Gateway: Order Created (HTTP 201)
                Gateway-->>Client: Success Response
            else Payment Failed
                Payment-->>Order: Payment Error
                Order->>Inventory: Release Items (Compensation)
                Order-->>Gateway: Payment Failed (HTTP 402)
                Gateway-->>Client: Error Response
            end

        else Inventory Unavailable
            Inventory-->>Order: Out of Stock
            Order-->>Gateway: Inventory Error (HTTP 409)
            Gateway-->>Client: Error Response
        end
    end
